original: Johnsson, Erik Wilhelm Gunnar, tandläkare, Eksjö, f. 17/6/96 i Åseda, Kronob. 1. — Stud:ex. i Växjö 17, tandl. 23. Prakt, i Storvik 23-29, därefter i Emmabo.da o. num. i Eksjö.
translated: Johnsson, Erik Wilhelm Gunnar, dentist, Eksjö, b. June 17, 1896 in Åseda, Kronob. - Graduated from Växjö high school in 1917, graduated from dental school in 1923. Worked as a dental practitioner in Storvik from 1923-1929, and then in Emmabo. Married in unknown year and partner's name. Continued working as a dental practitioner in Eksjö.
